headline: Generac (NYSE:GNRC) Misses Q4 Revenue Estimates
summary: Power generation products company Generac (NYSE:GNRC) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2024, but sales rose 16.1% year on year to $1.23 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.80 per share was 10.8% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
